                            <comment id="86424" author="miken" created="Mon, 31 Dec 2012 06:01:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seems to be a dupe with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6795&quot; title=&quot;provide AspectJ style configuration for exception translation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-6795&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-6795&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (couldn&apos;t find it earlier...), and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6282&quot; title=&quot;Enhance JPA Exception Translation to use PersistenceExceptionTranslator injected instance&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-6282&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-6282&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is a won&apos;t fix, but well... Implementation can be found in the description as a reference for other users...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
